metadata.name: Freedom
metadata.description:
It is such a passion to feed a pigeon, that it is very difficult to, explain and understand it...
It's like an unrequited love, feeding pigeons...
Maybe it's their free swing in the sky, playing games that attracts us..
We must not forget that we share this world withanimals.
Pigeons were effective in winning wars as homing pigeons in ancient times.  They can fly up to 1500 kilometers.
Feeding pigeons relaxes and reduces stress.  And if you train the pigeon when it's a baby, it will come to you.

Artist: Mehmet Karaca
Camera: Canon eos 70d 
Lens: Canon EF-S 10-18 MM F/4.5-5.6 IS STM
Dimensions: 3648x5472
Location: Kahramanmaras in TURKEY
Date: 12.01.2019
Edition: 1/1
